title: Designs for two frames
medium: Pen and black ink, traces of graphite, brush and wash, on white laid paper
description:
Horizontal rectangle showing two circular mirror frames, or plaques. Left: urn at top, cornucopia with flowers at either side from which are suspended garlands. 
Right: rollwork terminating in a volute at top, decorated with a flower garland and leaves. Black frame lines.
